\par\pard\plain \tx-720\sl240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 The role tab contains the information which defines the relationship between this character and the story.}
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 Unless your story's conception started with a particular character in mind, you should define the role before any other aspects of the character.}
